h answers to some of the most common information security questions  If you have any additional security questions  please contact the IT Help Desk at extension 7643  If you would like to report a potential information security violation contact the ITSO  REMEMBER  VMI s IT Department will never ask for your password  Contact Information The ITSO is dedicated to the task of securing VMI cadets  and employees  sensitive data and has helped to implement many internal security measures designed to prevent any such breaches of confidential information  If you believe you have witnessed a violation of VMI s Information Security Policy  want to report a data breach  or have additional questions for the ITSO  please call or contact ITSO  Major Douglas B  Wainwright ITSO Information Technology Virginia Military Institute Lexington  VA 24450  540  464 7725 VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu Virginia Military Institute   Information Security    Virginia Military Institute   Information Security                        skip to content VMI VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI Menu About About Us Administrative Offices Institute Report News  Photos  Videos VMI Archives Museums VMI Museum System The VMI Museum New Market Battlefield Stonewall Jackson House For Visitors Directions   Map Employment Parents   Family Conferences Chessie Nature Trail Bookstore Resources MyVMI Directories Friendly URLs Post